---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About | Astro Blog"
	description="Learn more about this blog and its author"
>
	<!--
		Prose container for styled markdown content
		prose: Enables Tailwind Typography plugin styles
		prose-lg: Larger prose sizing (18px base, matches our design)
		max-w-none: Allows prose to use full 650px width
	-->
	<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
		<!--
			Page heading
			font-sans: System fonts for UI
			text-4xl: Large heading (36px)
			font-bold: Bold weight
			text-dark-gray: Primary text color
			mb-8: 32px bottom margin
		-->
		<h1 class="font-sans text-4xl font-bold text-dark-gray mb-8">About</h1>

		<!--
			Article content
			text-lg: Larger text (18px)
			leading-relaxed: Comfortable line height (1.625)
		-->
		<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
			This is a minimalist blog built with Astro, designed for optimal reading experience.
		</p>

		<p>
			The design philosophy prioritizes typography, readability, and content over visual
			flourishes. Every element serves the purpose of helping you focus on the written word.
		</p>

		<h2 class="font-sans text-2xl font-bold text-dark-gray mt-8 mb-4">Design Principles</h2>

		<ul>
			<li><strong>Typography-first:</strong> Lora serif for body text, system fonts for UI</li>
			<li><strong>Optimal reading width:</strong> 650px max-width for ~70 characters per line</li>
			<li><strong>Comfortable spacing:</strong> Line height of 1.7-1.8 for easy reading</li>
			<li><strong>Minimal color palette:</strong> Warm off-white background, dark gray text, saddle brown accents</li>
			<li><strong>Content-focused:</strong> No hero images, no distractions, just great writing</li>
		</ul>

		<h2 class="font-sans text-2xl font-bold text-dark-gray mt-8 mb-4">Technical Stack</h2>

		<ul>
			<li><strong>Astro 5.x</strong> - Static site generator for fast, modern websites</li>
			<li><strong>Tailwind CSS 4.x</strong> - Utility-first CSS framework</li>
			<li><strong>Lora</strong> - Serif typeface optimized for screen reading</li>
			<li><strong>System fonts</strong> - Native fonts for fast-loading UI elements</li>
		</ul>

		<h2 class="font-sans text-2xl font-bold text-dark-gray mt-8 mb-4">About the Author</h2>

		<p>
			This is a placeholder for your personal bio. Replace this text with information about
			yourself, your background, and what you write about.
		</p>

		<p>
			You can find me on [Your Social Media Links Here].
		</p>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
